比如，就像你说的，你可以下载音乐或下载照片。

78
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:43,040
That means you find a photo on the internet that you like and you could save it on your
这意味着你在网上找到一张喜欢的照片，可以把它保存到你的

79
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,480
computer.
电脑上。

80
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,720
But you can also have a download.
但你也可以有“下载”这个名词。

81
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,160
So it can be a thing too.
所以它也可以是一样东西。

82
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,160
Okay.
好的。

83
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:53,600
So if maybe you're downloading three different files, you have three downloads.
所以如果你在下载三个不同的文件，你就有三个下载任务。

84
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:54,600
Okay.
好的。

85
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:57,320
So to download and download.
所以就是下载和下载。

86
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,320
Very good.
很好。

87
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:01,200
So now with internet, you have different speeds as we talked about, right?
那么现在有了互联网，就像我们之前聊的，有不同的速度，对吧？

88
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,880
How fast you're downloading something.
你下载东西的速度有多快。

89
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:06,000
And the guy mentioned 512 kbps.
那个人提到了512 kbps。

90
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,320
Oh no.
哦不。

91
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,560
Not another one of these kbps.
又来了一个kbps。

92
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,800
So this one, actually this was pretty simple.
这个其实挺简单的。

93
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,280
You can think about kilobytes.
你可以想想千字节。

94
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,280
You've heard about megabytes, kilobytes.
你听说过兆字节、千字节。

95
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:18,520
This is a size.
这是一个大小单位。

96
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:22,280
How fast you can receive these packets of information.
你接收这些信息包的速度有多快。

97
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:26,040
So 512 kilobytes per second.
所以是每秒512千字节。

98
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:30,080
Per second, that's, I have no idea how much that is.
每秒，那……我不知道那是多少。

99
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,080
It's maybe a lot.
可能挺多的。

100
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,080
It sounds like a lot.
听起来挺多的。

101
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,080
Right.
对。

102
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:38,240
Well, basically it is a lot, but we saw later that he was asking for a connection speed
嗯，基本上确实挺多的，但我们后来看到他要求的是连接速度

103
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,240
of two megabytes.
两兆字节。

104
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:42,560
Oh, so mega is bigger than kpbs, right?
哦，所以兆比kbps大，对吧？

105
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,560
Right.
对。

106
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,560
All right.
好的。

107
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:48,160
So these are different speeds of transferring information, right?
所以这些是传输信息的不同速度，对吧？

108
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:52,440
So this is a way for you to see what kind of internet plan you want.
所以这是让你了解自己想要哪种网络套餐的方式。

109
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,440
Exactly.
没错。

110
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:58,040
And so we have kilobytes, we have megabytes, and basically you want a faster connection
所以我们有千字节、兆字节，基本上你想要更快的连接

111
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:00,640
speed because you want to avoid lag.
速度，因为你想避免延迟。

112
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,360
Ooh, lag.
哦，延迟。

113
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,960
All right.
好的。

114
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:06,200
This is a word that you can use in a lot of different ways.
这个词可以用在很多不同的地方。

115
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:09,040
For example, my brother always lags behind.
比如，我哥哥总是落后。

116
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,040
Okay.
好的。

117
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,800
So it's a verb, but in this case we're talking about the noun.
所以它是动词，但在这里我们说的是名词。

118
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,280
So lag is slowness.
所以延迟就是缓慢。

119
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,280
Yeah.
是的。

120
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,280
It's like a delay.
就像一种延迟。

121
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,280
Yeah.
是啊。

122
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,480
It's a delay in something.
就是某件事有延迟。

123
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:23,520
So in this case, I can't even play my video games because there's too much lag.
所以在这种情况下，我连游戏都玩不了，因为延迟太高了。

124
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:25,600
So that means the internet's too slow.
那意味着网速太慢了。

125
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,600
Too slow.
太慢了。

126
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,600
Exactly.
没错。

127
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:30,900
So that's what happens when you have a slow connection speed, you have lag.
所以这就是连接速度慢时会发生的情况，你会遇到延迟。

128
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:34,480
And as you can say, it refers to something that's slow or delayed.
正如你所说，它指的是某件事缓慢或延迟。

129
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:39,760
So you can use it in other contexts when you want to say something is a little bit slow.
所以当你想说某件事有点慢时，可以在其他语境中使用它。

130
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:45,160
