嗯，另一个关键点是，当我们谈论互联网连接时，就是路由器。

131
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:50,880
So router is something that helps us to route an internet connection.
路由器是帮助我们路由互联网连接的东西。

132
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:53,040
So for example.
比如说。

133
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:58,520
So it basically distributes the internet connection to different computers or to different users.
它基本上将互联网连接分配给不同的电脑或不同的用户。

134
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:01,320
And some of these you plug in and some of them are wireless.
有些需要插线，有些是无线的。

135
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,760
That means without a wire.
意思是没有电线。

136
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:07,240
So a wireless router is something, a little box in your house that allows you to maybe
所以无线路由器就是你家里的一个小盒子，可以让你

137
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:11,800
have three or four computers on one broadband connection.
在一个宽带连接上使用三四台电脑。

138
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,800
Right.
对。

139
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,800
So it's very popular now.
现在很流行。

140
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:16,360
You go to Starbucks and you have Wi-Fi.
你去星巴克就有Wi-Fi。

141
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:20,920
In order to have Wi-Fi or wireless internet, you need a router, a wireless router.
要使用Wi-Fi或无线网络，你需要一个路由器，一个无线路由器。

142
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,920
Okay.
好的。

143
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,440
So wireless router.
所以是无线路由器。

144
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:27,360
