最后，什么东西可能会妨碍连接？

145
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,000
You have a firewall.
你有防火墙。

146
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,920
Very important security measure when navigating the internet.
上网时非常重要的安全措施。

147
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,920
All right.
好的。

148
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:36,560
So personal firewall is a firewall that you have on your computer to keep people from
个人防火墙就是你电脑上的一种防火墙，用来防止别人

149
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,680
spying on you.
监视你。

150
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:40,420
This keeps other people out.
它把其他人挡在外面。

151
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:41,420
So it's exactly that.
就是这样。

152
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:46,520
It's a wall between your computer and the outside world.
它是你电脑和外部世界之间的一堵墙。

153
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:50,960
So it protects you from any type of maybe malicious intruders.
所以它能保护你免受任何可能的恶意入侵者的侵害。

154
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:51,960
Right.
对。

155
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:59,120
And oftentimes governments and public offices, things like that, law offices, they have firewalls
而且通常政府、公共办公室、律师事务所之类的地方，他们都有防火墙

156
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:03,840
to protect the information that they store because it's so important that it's secretive.
来保护他们存储的信息，因为这些信息的保密性非常重要。

157
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,840
Yeah.
是啊。

158
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,840
So firewalls.
所以是防火墙。

159
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:09,960
There are many different types of firewalls, but a personal firewall is just a basic one.
防火墙有很多不同类型，但个人防火墙只是基本的一种。

160
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:10,960
Great.
太好了。

161
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:13,320
So that is our language takeaway for today.
这就是我们今天要学的语言点。

